it.uniud.mads.jlibbig.core.std

Interface Handle

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Handle, LinkEntity, Owned
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Edge, OuterName

    public interface Handle
extends Owned, LinkEntity, Handle
    Handles are link entities identifying the hyper-edges that compose link graphs and that link points. Handles are outer names or edges depending on whereas they belong to an outer interface or not.
